              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Challenge: Duplicate Payments Threatening Profitability</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">As a growing manufacturing company with multiple divisions, Midwest Manufacturing struggled with a decentralized purchasing process. The CFO discovered they had paid the same vendor twice for several large equipment purchases, resulting in over $60,000 in duplicate payments in just one quarter.</p>
              
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-6">Solution: Automated Detection & Prevention</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">After implementing RedFlag's spend analysis system, the company was able to:</p>
