                <li>Detect unusual payment patterns with key vendors</li>
                <li>Recover previously made duplicate payments</li>
                <li>Implement standardized procedures across all divisions</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p class="text-gray-600 italic mt-6">"RedFlag paid for itself within the first month. We not only stopped future duplicate payments but were able to recover funds from previous errors. The system flagged a pattern we would never have found manually." <span class="font-bold">- Sarah Chen, CFO</span></p>
