                <li>Significant price variations for identical materials</li>
                <li>Frequent small purchases instead of consolidated orders</li>
              </ul>
              
              <p class="text-gray-600 italic mt-6">"We knew we had waste in our procurement, but we couldn't pinpoint where. RedFlag showed us exactly where the money was going and helped us implement controls that dramatically improved our margins." <span class="font-bold">- James Wilson, Owner</span></p>
